            <div id="id3" style="height: 160px; left: 311px; position: absolute; top: 19px; width: 687px; z-index: 1; " class="style_SkipStroke_4 shape-with-text">
              <div class="text-content Normal_External_687_160" style="padding: 0px; ">
                <div class="Normal">
                  <p style="padding-top: 0pt; " class="paragraph_style_4">Problem Statement: 6 Dices tossed 6 times, and each time (or each set) a minimum is noted. What is expectation of maximum of these 6 minimum values.<br /></p>
                  <p class="paragraph_style_4"><br /></p>
                  <p style="padding-bottom: 0pt; " class="paragraph_style_4">Let's say I get for first set 1, 4, 6, 2, 3, 2 whose minimum is 1. This is repeated 6 times and let's say the set of minimums is {1,1,2,3,5,4} so maximum of this set is 5. I want to calculate the expectation of this maximum value. </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            


